					<font size="14" isBold="true" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Bold.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[5.1.4. Information on the primary venous whole blood samples and storage at the collection site:]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="90">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="90" uuid="cbc10c2b-3ecf-4b74-a3cc-0bdfab0497fe"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Since it is usually not clear which individual genomic DNA test will be performed after samples have been archived at a biobank, tubes with genomic DNA stabiliser should be used. If tubes without genomic DNA stabilisers are used, the recommendations for HMW DNA should be followed.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
